---
/**
 * Resumen: Sección informativa sobre mantenimiento de precisión.
 * Contenido: Texto explicativo sobre el uso de repuestos originales y una imagen técnica del taller.
 * Interacción: Imagen con efecto de escala de grises a color al hacer hover.
 */
---
<section class="mt-xl grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-lg items-center bg-white border border-outline-variant p-lg rounded">
  <div class="order-2 md:order-1">
    <h3 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-on-surface mb-md">Precision Maintenance</h3>
    <p class="text-body-lg text-on-surface-variant mb-lg">Our technicians use original BaByliss PRO components and
      specialized calibration tools to ensure your equipment performs like new. Every repair undergoes a 12-point
      inspection before release.</p>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 bg-surface-container-low border border-outline-variant rounded">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-sm">verified</span>
        <span class="text-label-md font-label-md uppercase">Original Parts</span>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 bg-surface-container-low border border-outline-variant rounded">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-sm">verified</span>
        <span class="text-label-md font-label-md uppercase">90-Day Warranty</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="order-1 md:order-2 h-64 md:h-full min-h-[300px] overflow-hidden rounded">
    <img alt="Technical Workshop"
      class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-700"
      src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida/ADBb0uikRC_WnFFjUPH36JrrBIQKsbYYQ76E1scgzwBeMjasEKS5guR522eusBa4MLH4qJtvHacRZhcHjepcJO57vR_BNQa_r6R93h2iblxyIHYWKHgg4QgLS-8vaQcy0PDErPNMW9SqT3qMb9zS1C9aDRH89Pro50aDHv_zhdtyEocSM3zQNKdwI0kGTf0rJLUDAUms-qX_WWcRRQZP4q0T60RCnqvwDPeKGxJ4OXHWTfMarF24dPqyvW1d5XnoSAW9FikM9e0vk0W6usw" />
  </div>
</section>
